Mini IMDB Clone

This is a Mini IMDB Clone app built with vanilla JavaScript. It allows users to search for movies using the OMDB API and displays search results. Users can add movies to their favorites list and view detailed information about each movie.

Features

Search movies: Users can enter a search query to find movies using the OMDB API. As they type, search suggestions are provided, and search results are displayed dynamically.
Movie details: Clicking on a search result opens a new page with detailed information about the selected movie, including its name, photo, plot, and other details.
Favorites list: Users can add movies to their favorites list by clicking the "Add to Favorites" button. The list is displayed on the same page and persists even after closing or refreshing the browser. Each movie in the favorites list can be removed by clicking the "Remove from Favorites" button.
Setup

To run the Mini IMDB Clone app locally, follow these steps:

Clone the repository or download the source code.
Open the index.html file in a web browser.
Dependencies

The Mini IMDB Clone app is built with the following dependencies:

Bootstrap (v4.3.1): Used for basic styling of the app.
